Miscellanea: epub

## epub file format

- Rename .epub to .zip and uncompress is
- Check images, resize, optimize...

To recompress the directory into a new book.epub:

    cd epub-contents
    
    # The file mimetype must go first and uncompressed
    zip -X0 book.epub mimetype
    
    # Add the rest excluding trash
    zip -rDX9 book.epub * -x "*.DS_Store" -x mimetype

You're done!

